---
title: American Fried Chicken & Buffalo Sauce with Crushed Potatoes & Cucumber Salad
description: Get ready to dig into this 5-star feast! Crispy, golden fried chicken drizzled with a homemade buffalo sauce brings the perfect mix of crunch and kick. Serve it up with crushed potatoes and a refreshing cucumber salad. Finger-lickin’ goodness guaranteed!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

